{"tid":2479564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"TVB新聞部到屯門友愛邨採訪 遭街坊指罵舉中指：食屎啦無綫","createTime":"2021-04-08T01:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-08T02:27:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7bf0241a03682cc7ccbb5672eae04227e4207c","tid":2479564,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:46:30.000Z","msg":"自從2019年香港發生逆權運動，無綫新聞在處理社會運動時屢被質疑內容偏頗，和港人的價值觀及信念背道而馳，網民甚至直接改稱TVB為「CCTVB」，意指TVB立場親中。今晚TVB派出採訪組，到屯門友愛邨採訪新增武漢肺炎個案的新聞，其間無綫記者李柔堃在現場做直播時，有街坊忽然大嗌「食屎啦無綫！」其聲量甚至蓋過拿着咪牌正在報道的李柔堃，同時一名在李柔堃身邊經過的男子，亦疑似對着鏡頭舉起中指。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210407/QFQR5FRZ2FDCNFIZDBECHK3BJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210407%2FQFQR5FRZ2FDCNFIZDBECHK3BJM%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=fc59e268\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210407%2FQFQR5FRZ2FDCNFIZDBECHK3BJM%2F&h=4f44ee38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210407/QFQR5FRZ2FDCNFIZDBECHK3BJM/</a>"},{"pid":"86dde8258bdb6bc501ff84041b36f7e239fa3cd5","tid":2479564,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:49:01.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"27fc40bb75e5a3c298efea7dfce69d4c8747eeaa","tid":2479564,"uid":217049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:49:19.000Z","msg":"「食屎啦無綫！」"},{"pid":"d85c9d4033348b6e80ec5199e64518c08bbd4a51","tid":2479564,"uid":190639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:50:14.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d817586078e5aafac5910792a83beeb302ac6eb6","tid":2479564,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:50:32.000Z","msg"